   {:e #blake3 "b5ef5a72405b3d1d9dda113e331931c3c38ecaf2190b8ab5d5036d185d155fcb" :a :task/description :v "CONTEXT: Tests for all 3 CCE-FIX implementations.\n\nUNIT TESTS (5 new tests):\n\n1. test_model2vec_join_threshold_value (CCE-FIX-1):\n   - Verify Embedder::join_threshold() returns 0.50.\n   - If cfg(feature=embeddings) not available, skip.\n\n2. test_narrow_candidates_collapsed (CCE-FIX-2):\n   - Setup: Store with 5 concepts, all with jaccard=1.00 (same member sets).\n   - Assert: narrow_candidates returns a FrontierRec with kind=Narrow and score > 0.\n   - Failure diagnostic: Log jaccard matrix and narrow candidate computation.\n\n3. test_narrow_candidates_healthy (CCE-FIX-2):\n   - Setup: Store with 3 concepts, jaccard < 0.3 between all pairs.\n   - Assert: narrow_candidates returns empty vec (no collapse detected).\n\n4. test_frontier_narrow_wins_over_generic (CCE-FIX-2):\n   - Setup: Store with collapsed concepts (jaccard > 0.8).\n   - Assert: frontier_recommendation returns Narrow, not Deepen/Bridge/Explore.\n\n5. test_innate_descriptions_no_shared_lead_words (CCE-FIX-3):\n   - Property: No two innate descriptions start with the same word.\n   - Iterate INNATE_CONCEPTS, collect first word of each description.\n   - Assert all first words are unique.\n\nE2E VERIFICATION:\n- Clear Go CLI store, fresh init, make 5 observations, verify:\n  (a) NOT all observations in all concepts (some should be uncategorized at threshold 0.50)\n  (b) Frontier recommendation shows Narrow or specific kind, not generic template\n  (c) Concept distribution has entropy > 0 after harvest\n\nDEPENDS-ON: CCE-FIX-1, CCE-FIX-2, CCE-FIX-3." :op :assert}
